{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"8d3afd6c-1450-47b7-8aa1-fcdf25df6765","content":"Here's the setup:\n\n**AppShell.xaml**\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<Shell x:Class=\"MyApp.AppShell\"\n       xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n       xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n       xmlns:views=\"clr-namespace:MyApp.Views\"\n       FlyoutBehavior=\"Flyout\">\n\n    <!-- Dashboard — single page, own flyout item -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Dashboard\" Icon=\"dashboard.png\">\n        <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:DashboardPage}\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Products — two tabs -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Products\" Icon=\"products.png\">\n        <Tab Title=\"Active\">\n            <ShellContent Title=\"Active\"\n                          ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ActiveProductsPage}\" />\n        </Tab>\n        <Tab Title=\"Archived\">\n            <ShellContent Title=\"Archived\"\n                          ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ArchivedProductsPage}\" />\n        </Tab>\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Settings — separate flyout entry -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Settings\" Icon=\"settings.png\">\n        <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:SettingsPage}\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n</Shell>\n```\n\n**AppShell.xaml.cs** — register the detail route:\n```csharp\nnamespace MyApp;\n\npublic partial class AppShell : Shell\n{\n    public AppShell()\n    {\n        InitializeComponent();\n\n        // Register route for programmatic navigation\n        Routing.RegisterRoute(nameof(Views.ProductDetailsPage),\n                              typeof(Views.ProductDetailsPage));\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Navigating to the detail page** (e.g. from a list item tap):\n```csharp\nawait Shell.Current.GoToAsync($\"{nameof(ProductDetailsPage)}?id={product.Id}\");\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n| Concept | What it does |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `FlyoutItem` | Top-level entry in the flyout menu |\n| `Tab` inside a `FlyoutItem` | Creates bottom tabs within that section |\n| `Routing.RegisterRoute` | Enables `GoToAsync` navigation to pages not in the visual hierarchy |\n| `ContentTemplate` + `DataTemplate` | Lazy-loads pages on first visit |\n\nThe `Products` flyout item will show a bottom tab bar with \"Active\" and \"Archived\" when selected. `ProductDetailsPage` is pushed onto the navigation stack from either tab via its registered route.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"8ee56c2c-f84b-4647-8a67-f2dadb5adecc","outputTokens":664,"requestId":"9435:353499:13937B2:15EBE50:6A066E86"},"id":"36ef7eb4-7515-4e1d-9a87-b47a5a3a048d","timestamp":"2026-05-15T00:53:39.434Z","parentId":"e8d6fa29-4a7c-4c63-a46d-87491b53f98c"}
